Solved the torchtext installing issue:
Environment: Windows 10 Pro, Pytorch 1.11.0, cuda 11.6

use following cmd in prompt with admin:
conda install pytorch torchvision torchaudio cudatoolkit=11.3 -c pytorch (11.3 and 11.6 doesnt matter)
>>> import torchtext
>>> print(torchtext.__version__)
0.12.0
>>>
解决了torchtext v0.12 安装



Solved the torch.data has no Field in v0.12 issue:

just add "from torchtext.legacy import data, datasets" at the beginning
although in pytorch v0.12 release manual, they claimed that they deleted the legacy folder, but in fact, it is still there

to use Field just:

SRC_TEXT = data.Field(sequential=True,
                                tokenize=tokenizer,
                                # lower=True,
                                fix_length=MAX_LENGTH + 2,
                                preprocessing=lambda x: ['<start>'] + x + ['<end>'],
                                # after tokenizing but before numericalizing
                                # postprocessing # after numericalizing but before the numbers are turned into a Tensor
                                )
解决了 v0.12版本的 torchtext 找不到 torchtext.legacy.data.Field的问题
